<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style type="text/css">
        *{
            margin:0;
            padding:0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .wrapper{
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box">
    <div class="wrapper">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 1.3rem;">HI TOBI!</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1.3rem;">
            I hope this message finds you well. We have an event coming up and we are in search of a talented and experienced DJ to make our event truly unforgettable. 
            After researching various DJs, your exceptional skills and reputation caught our attention and we believe you would be the perfect fit for our event.
        </p>
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.9rem;">EVENT DETAILS:</h3>
        <ul style="margin-bottom: 1.3rem;">
            <li><span style="font-weight: 600; font-size:0.85rem;">EVENT NAME:</span> <%=eventName%>.</li>
            <li><span style="font-weight: 600; font-size:0.85rem;">DESCRIPTION:</span> <%= description %>.</li>
            <li><span style="font-weight: 600; font-size:0.85rem;">TYPE:</span> <%= type %>.</li>
            <li><span style="font-weight: 600; font-size:0.85rem;">DATE:</span> <%= myDate %>.</li>
            <li><span style="font-weight: 600; font-size:0.85rem;">VENUE:</span> <%= location %>.</li>
            <li><span style="font-weight: 600; font-size:0.85rem;">EXPECTED GUESTS:</span> <%= expectedGuests %>.</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1.3rem">
            If you are available on <%= myDate %> and interested in being part of our event, please let us know your availability and pricing.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0.9rem;">Warm regards,</p>

        <h4>NAME: <%= name %></h4>
        <h4>COMPANY's NAME: <%= companyName %></h4>
        <h4>EMAIL: <%= email %></h4>
    </div>
</body>
</html>